That went well.

280
00:15:41,343 --> 00:15:43,066
What an amazing car.

281
00:15:43,091 --> 00:15:45,553
If you like it, I'll give you a ride anytime.

282
00:15:45,612 --> 00:15:47,085
Or buy you one of your own.

283
00:15:47,376 --> 00:15:50,218
By the way, loving that nurse's outfit, Misa.

284
00:15:50,321 --> 00:15:51,765
I'm glad you like it.

285
00:15:54,245 --> 00:15:55,445
That took a while.

286
00:16:02,526 --> 00:16:03,239
Ah!

287
00:16:04,051 --> 00:16:04,911
