290
00:16:19,721 --> 00:16:21,298
Kyosuke Higuchi.

291
00:16:21,806 --> 00:16:25,598
The sleazy pervert who's been sending
me text messages ever since that party.

292
00:16:25,623 --> 00:16:28,594
He's been even more persistent than any of the other guys.

293
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:30,406
He's Kira?

294
00:16:30,587 --> 00:16:32,484
It can't get any worse than that.

295
00:16:33,921 --> 00:16:34,687
Hey, Misa?

296
00:16:34,712 --> 00:16:35,075
Huh?

297
00:16:35,227 --> 00:16:36,723
How about we grab a bite to eat?

298
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:41,716
