somewhere and do pervy things to me?

299
00:16:41,819 --> 00:16:44,019
Well, even if you are, that's OK.

300
00:16:44,044 --> 00:16:45,989
I'll be fine. Since I can kill people.

301
00:16:49,459 --> 00:16:51,056
What are you saying, Misa?

302
00:16:51,192 --> 00:16:53,373
Is this part of Light Yagami's plan?

303
00:16:53,617 --> 00:16:55,494
Is this what he wants you to do?

304
00:16:55,982 --> 00:16:59,435
Or is this your way of telling
me that you want me to kill Higuchi

305
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:01,280
the moment he tries to do anything?

306
00:17:02,583 --> 00:17:05,015
Come on, you're just getting with me, aren't you, Misa?

307
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:06,545
You can kill people?

308
00:17:06,843 --> 00:17:08,304
Yep. It's true.

309
00:17:08,370 --> 00:17:09,593
And you know why?

310
00:17:10,132 --> 00:17:12,237
Because I'm the second Kira.

311
00:17:13,716 --> 00:17:14,874
That can't be.

312
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:17,379
Even if she was the second Kira before,

313
00:17:17,404 --> 00:17:19,059
there's no way she still is.

314
00:17:19,313 --> 00:17:21,643
She's not supposed to have any memory of it, either.

315
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,925
What the hell's going on?

316
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:25,848
Oh, Misa.

317
00:17:26,136 --> 00:17:29,074
You don't have to make up stuff
like that to feel safe with me.

318
00:17:29,099 --> 00:17:31,656
I'm sure you'll find that I'm quite the gentleman.

319
00:17:31,681 --> 00:17:33,250
Yeah, maybe.

320
00:17:33,337 --> 00:17:37,129
Anyway, I'll only prove that I'm
the second Kira to the real Kira.

321
00:17:37,288 --> 00:17:39,188
You'll only show proof to Kira?

322
00:17:39,323 --> 00:17:39,968
Why?

323
00:17:41,127 --> 00:17:44,932
I'd show him because it's always
been my dream to become Kira's wife.

324
00:17:44,983 --> 00:17:47,602
I know he'll need me by his side once I tell him.

325
00:17:48,766 --> 00:17:50,860
If she really is the second Kira,

326
00:17:50,987 --> 00:17:55,528
then it's pretty clear from the Sakura TV
incident that she has the Shinigami eyes.

327
00:17:55,888 --> 00:17:59,608
If that's the case, I need to make
sure I keep this girl by my side.

328
00:17:59,728 --> 00:18:00,967
At all costs.

329
00:18:01,401 --> 00:18:03,377
I've got to test her, first.

330
00:18:06,930 --> 00:18:11,310
Well, since I happen to be Kira,
does that mean you'll marry me?

331
00:18:14,579 --> 00:18:15,129
Hm?

332
00:18:17,171 --> 00:18:18,320
Really?

333
00:18:19,054 --> 00:18:19,801
Yeah.

334
00:18:20,495 --> 00:18:21,320
I mean it.

335
00:18:21,616 --> 00:18:22,516
What?

336
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:23,641
Then prove it to me.

337
00:18:23,666 --> 00:18:25,366
Come on, let's prove it to each other.

338
00:18:25,636 --> 00:18:26,935
I can't do that.

339
00:18:27,372 --> 00:18:30,451
It'd be a pretty bad idea to let
someone witness how I kill people.

340
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:31,880
You think so?

341
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:35,011
I dunno. I thought someone was Kira,

342
00:18:35,036 --> 00:18:36,612
I think I'd be willing to show them.

343
00:18:36,694 --> 00:18:39,285
We'd never get anywhere if I didn't.

344
00:18:39,577 --> 00:18:41,141
Then why don't you kill someone?

345
00:18:41,452 --> 00:18:43,612
After all, I could be the real Kira.

346
00:18:43,889 --> 00:18:46,829
All right. But I only kill bad people, OK?

347
00:18:47,076 --> 00:18:47,970
That's right.

348
00:18:48,288 --> 00:18:49,639
Bad person, huh?

349
00:18:52,625 --> 00:18:57,318
This is Ginzo Kaneboshi,
president of a major finance company.

350
00:18:57,343 --> 00:18:59,670
He's infamous for his immoral collection methods.

351
00:18:59,695 --> 00:19:02,717
Sometimes he even makes people
pay with their insurance money.

352
00:19:02,829 --> 00:19:03,539
How about him?

353
00:19:03,564 --> 00:19:06,150
Would you be able to confirm his death right away?

354
00:19:06,175 --> 00:19:07,722
Yeah. As soon as I call him.

355
00:19:07,908 --> 00:19:09,044
OK, then.

356
00:19:09,228 --> 00:19:11,085
Could you turn around for just a sec?

357
00:19:14,792 --> 00:19:15,774
Misa.

358
00:19:15,982 --> 00:19:19,215
You want me to kill Ginzo Kaneboshi, don't you?

359
00:19:19,536 --> 00:19:23,340
Then Higuchi will believe your
claim about being the second Kira.

360
00:19:23,862 --> 00:19:24,744
Very well.

361
00:19:26,876 --> 00:19:28,882
All right. He should be dead by now.

362
00:19:31,849 --> 00:19:33,320
Hello, this is Higuchi from Yotsuba.

363
00:19:33,345 --> 00:19:35,676
Sorry. Our president just collapsed and stopped breathing.

364
00:19:35,701 --> 00:19:36,709
Call back later.

365
00:19:43,923 --> 00:19:44,777
Told ya.

366
00:19:45,870 --> 00:19:47,317
She killed him.

367
00:19:48,098 --> 00:19:50,599
The same guy I chose just a minute ago.

368
00:19:51,298 --> 00:19:54,142
