do that unless she had the power.

369
00:19:54,354 --> 00:19:55,446
This proves it.

370
00:20:01,883 --> 00:20:04,801
So. If I'm Kira, you'll marry me, right?

371
00:20:05,414 --> 00:20:09,169
Wha Hey, why are you getting so serious all of a sudden?

372
00:20:09,737 --> 00:20:11,240
Because I'm Kira.

373
00:20:11,305 --> 00:20:12,519
Then prove it.

374
00:20:12,818 --> 00:20:13,465
Hm.

375
00:20:13,672 --> 00:20:16,231
I'm not going to be able to kill until I get home.

376
00:20:16,650 --> 00:20:17,873
You understand?

377
00:20:18,606 --> 00:20:21,085
Oh, well, that's no good then.

378
00:20:21,406 --> 00:20:26,283
For all I know, you're just making all this up
so you have an excuse to take me to your place.

379
00:20:26,321 --> 00:20:27,405
Wait! I know.

380
00:20:27,490 --> 00:20:28,046
Huh?

381
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:30,948
Why don't you stop killing the criminals on TV.

382
00:20:30,973 --> 00:20:32,016
That should prove it.

383
00:20:32,041 --> 00:20:34,092
If you're Kira, it should be no problem.

384
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,853
You can start killing again when I tell you to.

385
00:20:36,905 --> 00:20:38,641
If all the times and deaths match up,

386
00:20:38,666 --> 00:20:39,655
then I'll believe you.

387
00:20:40,196 --> 00:20:43,747
After all, killing criminals in that
way is something that only Kira can do.

388
00:20:44,856 --> 00:20:46,156
I see what you mean.

389
00:20:46,254 --> 00:20:47,641
That's a good idea.

390
00:20:48,858 --> 00:20:50,058
All right, Misa.

391
00:20:50,083 --> 00:20:53,576
I'm Kira, so in order to make
you trust me and prove that I'm him,

392
00:20:53,601 --> 00:20:56,227
I'll stop killing criminals for the time being.

393
00:20:56,252 --> 00:20:58,580
Then, once you're fully convinced I'm the real thing,

394
00:20:58,605 --> 00:21:00,314
you and I can get married.

395
00:21:02,296 --> 00:21:06,465
And so, based on what he said, Higuchi is Kira!

396
00:21:08,038 --> 00:21:10,224
Now we not only know Kira's identity,

397
00:21:10,289 --> 00:21:13,236
but all those deaths that were
worrying the chief are gonna stop!

398
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:14,949
That's amazing, Misa Misa!

399
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:39,725
It's been three days since I stopped killing criminals.

400
00:22:39,778 --> 00:22:41,233
That should be good enough.

401
00:22:41,258 --> 00:22:44,291
Now if I marry Misa Amane, the second Kira,

402
00:22:44,369 --> 00:22:46,321
I'll have the Shinigami eyes.

403
00:22:46,346 --> 00:22:50,044
With that power, Yotsuba will be under my control.

